imdb.plot outline: Kambal, karibal is the story of two twins Criselda and Crisanta. Criselda dies from a rare disease and remains as a spirit that only Crisanta can see. Their close bond starts to fall apart when they both fall in love with a boy name Diego. Eventually, Criselda inhabits a new person's body and she will stop at nothing to win Diego's love.
imdb.title: Kambal, karibal
plot: _Kambal, karibal_ (qv) is the story of two twins Criselda and Crisanta. Criselda dies from a rare disease and remains as a spirit that only Crisanta can see. Their close bond starts to fall apart when they both fall in love with a boy name Diego. Eventually, Criselda inhabits a new person's body and she will stop at nothing to win Diego's love.
